        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>
                <p>Magic prayer against demons as well as against various diseases which are named as Bāryā, Legewon, migraine, colic, chest pain, 
                    rheumatism, Budā, Falašā, Gudale, Dabbās, and all diseases by the help of <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr">ʾasmāt</foreign> (magic
                    names), which are placed as enforcement before the exhortation and which are identical or similar to 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr">ʾasmāt</foreign> or <foreign xml:lang="gez-tr">qālāt</foreign> in 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6851Prayer">Prayer against the sufferings provoked by the Budā, containing
          ʾasmāt</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP00616">EMIP00616</ref>.</p>
            </abstract>
